<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to Sendora!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #0D99FF;
      margin: 0;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #0D99FF;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #007dd6;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="Sendora Logo" class="logo" />
      <h2>Welcome to Sendora!</h2>
    </div>

    <p>Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>

    <p>We're excited to have you on board. Start sending parcels with ease, speed, and reliability.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out.</p>

    <a href="https://sendora.example.com" class="btn">Visit Dashboard</a>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Sendora Courier. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
